                                        GHS <span t-esc="'{:,.2f}'.format((o.ssnit_employee or 0) + (o.ssnit_employer or 0))"/>
                                    </td>
                                </tr>
                            </table>
                            <p style="margin: 10px 0 0 0; font-size: 0.85em; color: #856404;">
                                <em>* Maximum insurable income: GHS 5,083.33 per month (GHS 61,000 annually)</em>
                            </p>
